create_complex_test_file()
db = dapt.Delimited_file('test.csv', ',')
param = dapt.Param(db)
actual = param.next_parameters()
expected = actual
actual = param.failed(actual['id'], 'This is an error')
expected = OrderedDict({'id': 't2', 'start-time': '', 'end-time': '',
    'status': 'failed', 'comment': '', 'performed-by': '', 'a': '10', 'b':
    '10', 'c': ''})
if (datetime.datetime.strptime(datetime.datetime.now().strftime(
    '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S') - datetime.datetime.strptime
    (actual['start-time'], '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')).seconds < 15:
    expected['start-time'] = actual['start-time']
if (datetime.datetime.strptime(datetime.datetime.now().strftime(
    '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S') - datetime.datetime.strptime
    (actual['end-time'], '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')).seconds < 15:
    expected['end-time'] = actual['end-time']
assert actual == expected, 'Cannot update the status of the paramater set.'
